<h3><strong>GET</strong> <code>/api/conversations/{id}</code> ðŸ”’</h3>
<p>Returns the specified message if the user has access to it</p>

<h3><strong>GET</strong> <code>/api/conversations/</code> ðŸ”’</h3>
<p>Returns an array with all the conversations this user has access to</p>

<h3><strong>GET</strong> <code>/api/conversations/unread</code> ðŸ”’</h3>
<p>Returns an array with all the conversations with unread messages</p>

<h3><strong>POST</strong> <code>/api/conversations/</code> ðŸ”’</h3>
<p>Creates a new conversation with a user if one doesn't exist already</p>
<h4>Request body</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>recipient</strong>: ID of the other user who'll be a member of this conversation</li>
</ul>


<h3><strong>PUT</strong> <code>/api/conversations/{id}</code> ðŸ”’</h3>
<p>Updates the information of a specific conversation</p>
<h4>Request body</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>backgroundImg (optional)</strong></li>
  <li><strong>backgroundColor (optional)</strong></li>
</ul>

<h3><strong>DELETE</strong> <code>/api/conversations/{id}</code> ðŸ”’</h3>
<p>Deletes the specified conversation</p>
